(509, 125, 'content_blocks_0_content_block', '<div class=\"title-area\">\r\n    <span class=\"pre-title\">\r\n        Legal Assistant\r\n    </span>\r\n    <h3 class=\"title animated fadeIn\">\r\n        Serena Yerevanian\r\n    </h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Serena is a dedicated and motivated Legal Assistant at Capital Street Law With a background in Law and Society from York University, Serena brings a strong foundation in legal principles and a passion for the field of law to support the team. Serena graduated from York University with a bachelorâs degree in law and Society with honours. Through her studies, she has gained a comprehensive understanding of legal systems, social justice, and the impact of law on society. Serena continues to broaden her knowledge and skills in the legal field to better serve our clients.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    As a Legal Assistant at Capital Street Law Serena plays a crucial role in providing administrative and legal support to our team of attorneys. She assists with legal research, document preparation, file management, and client communications. Serena\'s attention to detail, organizational skills, and strong work ethic contribute to the smooth functioning of our firm.\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"disc\">\r\n    Serena understands the importance of providing exceptional service to our clients. She prioritizes client satisfaction by ensuring prompt and accurate support, maintaining confidentiality, and demonstrating professionalism in all interactions. Serena strives to contribute to the positive experience our clients have with our firm and is ready to assist our clients any way she can.\r\n</p>'),
