(3597, 103, 'service_details_card_0_card_title', 'Divorce and Separation:'),
(3598, 103, '_service_details_card_0_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3599, 103, 'service_details_card_0_card_content', 'Our family law team is well-versed in handling divorce and separation cases. We recognize that this is a difficult time for you and your family, and we strive to minimize conflict while protecting your interests. Whether your divorce is amicable or contentious, we will work diligently to negotiate fair settlements or represent you in court if necessary. Our focus is on achieving the best possible outcome for you and your children.'),
(3600, 103, '_service_details_card_0_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3601, 103, 'service_details_card_1_card_title', 'Decision-making Responsibility and Parenting time (formerly custody and access):'),
(3602, 103, '_service_details_card_1_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3603, 103, 'service_details_card_1_card_content', 'When it comes to child custody, we prioritize the best interests of the children involved. Our lawyers have extensive experience in developing decision-making responsibility and parenting time arrangements that promote stability and ensure a healthy environment for your children.'),
(3604, 103, '_service_details_card_1_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3605, 103, 'service_details_card_2_card_title', 'Child Support:'),
(3606, 103, '_service_details_card_2_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3607, 103, 'service_details_card_2_card_content', 'Child support is the financial support provided by one parent to the other for the benefit of their children. It is intended to cover expenses such as education, healthcare, childcare, and general living costs. Our lawyers work closely with clients to calculate child support based on relevant guidelines and factors, ensuring that the best interests of the child are prioritized. We also assist in modifying existing child support orders when circumstances change, such as income adjustments or significant life events.'),
(3608, 103, '_service_details_card_2_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3609, 103, 'service_details_card_3_card_title', 'Spousal Support:'),
(3610, 103, '_service_details_card_3_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3611, 103, 'service_details_card_3_card_content', 'Spousal support, also known as alimony or maintenance, refers to the financial support provided by one spouse to the other after separation or divorce. The purpose of spousal support is to address any disparities in income, earning capacity, or financial resources between the spouses. Our lawyers assess the unique circumstances of each case and advocate for fair and equitable spousal support arrangements. We guide clients through negotiation, mediation, or litigation, depending on the situation, to achieve the most favorable outcome.'),
(3612, 103, '_service_details_card_3_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3613, 103, 'service_details_card_4_card_title', 'Adoption:'),
(3614, 103, '_service_details_card_4_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3615, 103, 'service_details_card_4_card_content', 'Adopting a child is a beautiful and life-changing experience. Our family law team is dedicated to guiding you through the adoption process, providing comprehensive legal assistance at every step. We handle all types of adoptions, including domestic, international, stepparent, and relative adoptions. From completing the necessary paperwork to representing you in court, we will ensure a smooth and successful adoption journey.'),
(3616, 103, '_service_details_card_4_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3617, 103, 'service_details_card_5_card_title', 'Prenuptial, Separation and Parenting Agreements:'),
(3618, 103, '_service_details_card_5_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3619, 103, 'service_details_card_5_card_content', 'Protecting your assets and addressing financial matters before or during marriage is a wise decision. Our lawyers can help you draft prenuptial or separation agreements that establish clear guidelines for property division, spousal support, and other financial matters. We will work closely with you to ensure the agreement reflects your intentions and protects your interests.'),
(3620, 103, '_service_details_card_5_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3621, 103, 'service_details_card_6_card_title', 'Spousal Support:'),
(3622, 103, '_service_details_card_6_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3623, 103, 'service_details_card_6_card_content', 'Spousal support, also known as alimony or maintenance, refers to the financial support provided by one spouse to the other after separation or divorce. The purpose of spousal support is to address any disparities in income, earning capacity, or financial resources between the spouses. Our lawyers assess the unique circumstances of each case and advocate for fair and equitable spousal support arrangements. We guide clients through negotiation, mediation, or litigation, depending on the situation, to achieve the most favorable outcome.\r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n\r\nA parenting agreement, also known as a parenting plan or custody agreement, is a legal document that outlines the rights and responsibilities of parents regarding their children after separation or divorce. At Capital Street Law, we understand the importance of creating a comprehensive and child-centered parenting agreement that serves the best interests of your children.'),
(3624, 103, '_service_details_card_6_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3625, 103, 'service_details_card_7_card_title', 'Domestic Violence and Restraining Orders:'),
(3626, 103, '_service_details_card_7_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3627, 103, 'service_details_card_7_card_content', 'If you or your loved ones are facing domestic violence, our family law team is here to offer immediate assistance and protection. We understand the urgency of these situations and will take swift action to help you obtain restraining orders and other legal remedies to ensure your safety.'),
(3628, 103, '_service_details_card_7_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3629, 103, 'service_details_card', '8'),
(3630, 103, '_service_details_card', 'field_64a7e5d41bb8d'),
