(3813, 115, 'intro_description', 'At Capital Street Law, our experienced team of criminal defense lawyers is dedicated to providing strong legal representation and advocacy for individuals facing criminal charges. We understand the seriousness of criminal allegations and the potential impact they can have on your life. Our goal is to protect your rights, ensure a fair legal process, and seek the best possible outcome for your case.'),
(3814, 115, '_intro_description', 'field_64a7e528cb03c'),
(3815, 115, 'intro', ''),
(3816, 115, '_intro', 'field_64a7da3d85a48'),
(3817, 115, 'service_details_card_0_card_title', 'Legal Expertise:'),
(3818, 115, '_service_details_card_0_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3819, 115, 'service_details_card_0_card_content', 'Our lawyers have a deep understanding of criminal law and extensive experience defending clients in a wide range of criminal cases. We handle various types of charges, including but not limited to drug offenses, assault, theft, white-collar crimes, DUI/DWI, domestic violence, and juvenile offenses. We provide personalized attention and tailor our approach to the specific circumstances of your case.'),
(3820, 115, '_service_details_card_0_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3821, 115, 'service_details_card_1_card_title', 'Comprehensive Defense Strategies:'),
(3822, 115, '_service_details_card_1_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3823, 115, 'service_details_card_1_card_content', 'We develop comprehensive defense strategies tailored to the unique aspects of your case. Our lawyers conduct thorough investigations, analyze evidence, and assess the strengths and weaknesses of the prosecutionâs case. We strive to uncover any constitutional violations, procedural errors, or weaknesses in the evidence to build a strong defense on your behalf.'),
(3824, 115, '_service_details_card_1_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3825, 115, 'service_details_card_2_card_title', 'Legal Guidance and Representation:'),
(3826, 115, '_service_details_card_2_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3827, 115, 'service_details_card_2_card_content', 'Throughout the criminal justice process, we provide clear and straightforward legal guidance to help you understand your rights, options, and potential outcomes. We communicate with you regularly, keeping you informed about the progress of your case and ensuring that you are actively involved in decision-making. Our lawyers vigorously advocate for you in negotiations, hearings, and, if necessary, in trial proceedings.'),
(3828, 115, '_service_details_card_2_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3829, 115, 'service_details_card_3_card_title', 'Pre-Trial Representation:'),
(3830, 115, '_service_details_card_3_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3831, 115, 'service_details_card_3_card_content', 'We provide aggressive representation during the pre-trial phase, aiming to have charges dismissed or reduced when possible. Our lawyers negotiate with prosecutors, challenge evidence, file pre-trial motions, and explore alternatives to trial, such as diversion programs or plea negotiations. We work diligently to protect your rights and achieve the most favorable outcome before trial.'),
(3832, 115, '_service_details_card_3_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3833, 115, 'service_details_card_4_card_title', 'Trial Defense:'),
(3834, 115, '_service_details_card_4_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3835, 115, 'service_details_card_4_card_content', 'If your case proceeds to trial, our experienced trial lawyers will skillfully present your defense in the courtroom. We meticulously prepare your case, conduct witness examinations, cross-examine the prosecutionâs witnesses, and present compelling arguments on your behalf. Our goal is to challenge the prosecutionâs case and create reasonable doubt in the minds of the jurors.'),
(3836, 115, '_service_details_card_4_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3837, 115, 'service_details_card_5_card_title', 'Appeals and Post-Conviction Relief:'),
(3838, 115, '_service_details_card_5_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3839, 115, 'service_details_card_5_card_content', 'If you have been convicted of a crime, our lawyers can assist you with the appeals process and post-conviction relief efforts. We review trial records, identify potential legal errors, and pursue avenues for appealing your conviction or seeking post-conviction remedies. Our focus is to ensure that your rights are protected and to explore all available options for relief.\r\n\r\n'),
(3840, 115, '_service_details_card_5_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3841, 115, 'service_details_card_6_card_title', 'Client-Centered Approach:'),
(3842, 115, '_service_details_card_6_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3843, 115, 'service_details_card_6_card_content', 'We understand the emotional and personal impact that criminal charges can have on your life. Our lawyers provide compassionate support, listen to your concerns, and treat you with respect and dignity. We are committed to guiding you through this challenging time and providing you with the dedicated representation you deserve.\r\n\r\n'),
(3844, 115, '_service_details_card_6_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3845, 115, 'service_details_card', '7'),
(3846, 115, '_service_details_card', 'field_64a7e5d41bb8d'),
(3847, 115, 'outro_0_outro_description', 'If you are facing criminal charges or require legal assistance in a criminal matter, contact Capital Street Law today to schedule a consultation with one of our experienced criminal defense lawyers. We will assess your case, answer your questions, and work tirelessly to protect your rights and achieve the best possible outcome in your situation.'),
(3848, 115, '_outro_0_outro_description', 'field_64a7f03dcc126'),
(3849, 115, 'outro', '1'),
(3850, 115, '_outro', 'field_64a7f012cc125'),
(3851, 116, 'intro_description', 'At Capital Street Law, we understand the importance of planning for the future and ensuring that your assets and loved ones are protected. Our experienced team of estate planning lawyers is dedicated to providing comprehensive legal guidance in wills, estates, and trusts. We work closely with our clients to develop personalized plans that reflect their wishes, protect their assets, and provide for their families and beneficiaries.'),
(3852, 116, '_intro_description', 'field_64a7e528cb03c'),
(3853, 116, 'intro', ''),
(3854, 116, '_intro', 'field_64a7da3d85a48'),
(3855, 116, 'service_details_card_0_card_title', 'Estate Planning:'),
(3856, 116, '_service_details_card_0_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3857, 116, 'service_details_card_0_card_content', 'Our lawyers assist individuals and families in creating comprehensive estate plans tailored to their unique circumstances. We guide you through the process of drafting wills, establishing trusts, and implementing other essential estate planning documents. Our goal is to minimize potential disputes, reduce tax liabilities, and ensure the smooth transfer of assets to your chosen beneficiaries.\r\n\r\n'),
(3858, 116, '_service_details_card_0_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3859, 116, 'service_details_card_1_card_title', 'Will Drafting and Probate:'),
(3860, 116, '_service_details_card_1_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3861, 116, 'service_details_card_1_card_content', 'We provide professional will drafting services to ensure that your final wishes are clearly and legally documented. Our lawyers work with you to understand your objectives and create wills that address your specific concerns. We also offer guidance on probate matters, assisting executors and beneficiaries in navigating the probate process efficiently and effectively.\r\n\r\n'),
(3862, 116, '_service_details_card_1_card_content', 'field_64a7e60f1bb8f'),
(3863, 116, 'service_details_card_2_card_title', 'Trust Formation and Administration:'),
(3864, 116, '_service_details_card_2_card_title', 'field_64a7e6031bb8e'),
(3865, 116, 'service_details_card_2_card_content', ' <p class=\"disc\">\r\n                    We help clients establish various types of trusts, such as revocable living trusts, irrevocable trusts, and special needs trusts. Trusts can offer numerous benefits, including asset protection, privacy, and avoidance of probate. Our lawyers provide guidance on selecting the right type of trust for your needs and assist in the proper administration and management of trusts.\r\n                </p>\r\n\r\n                <div class=\"service-detials-step-3\">\r\n                    <div class=\"row g-5 align-items-center mt--5\">\r\n                        <div class=\"col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-12 mb_md--20 mb_sm--20\">\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\"            style=\"display: flex;\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"      style=\"margin: 6px 10px auto 5px;\" ></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Express Trust: </b>\r\n                                    This is a trust created intentionally by the settlor (the person creating the trust) through a written trust document or a will. The express trust can be established during the settlor\'s lifetime (inter vivos trust) or upon their death (testamentary trust).\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Family Trust:</b>\r\n                                    A family trust is created for the benefit of family members, such as spouses, children, or grandchildren. It is commonly used for estate planning purposes, asset protection, and wealth transfer within the family.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Testamentary Trust:</b>\r\n                                    This type of trust is established through a person\'s will and comes into effect upon their death. Testamentary trusts are often used to provide for minor children, and individuals with disabilities, or to control the distribution of assets over time.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Living Trust:</b>\r\n                                    Also known as an inter vivos trust, a living trust is created during the settlor\'s lifetime. It allows the settlor to transfer assets into the trust while maintaining control over them during their lifetime. Living trusts can be revocable (modifiable) or irrevocable (non-modifiable).\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Charitable Trust:</b>\r\n                                    A charitable trust is created for charitable purposes, such as supporting a specific cause, funding research, or advancing education. It allows individuals to donate assets or funds to a charitable organization and receive potential tax benefits.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Special Needs Trust:</b>\r\n                                    This type of trust is established to provide for the financial well-being of an individual with special needs or disabilities. It is designed to supplement government benefits and ensure that the beneficiary\'s needs are met without jeopardizing their eligibility for social assistance.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Discretionary Trust:</b>\r\n                                    In a discretionary trust, the trustee has discretion in determining how and when to distribute the trust assets to the beneficiaries. This type of trust allows flexibility in distributing income or assets based on the beneficiaries\' needs and circumstances.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Spendthrift Trust:</b>    \r\n                                    A spendthrift trust is created to protect the assets held within the trust from the beneficiaries\' creditors. It restricts the beneficiary\'s ability to transfer or assign their interest in the trust and safeguards the assets from potential financial risks.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Resulting Trust:</b>\r\n                                    A resulting trust arises when property is held by one person but is intended for the benefit of another. It occurs when a person holds property on behalf of another due to a presumed or implied intention.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            <div class=\"single-banifits\">\r\n                                <i class=\"far fa-check-circle\"></i>\r\n                                <span>\r\n                                    <b>Constructive Trust:</b>\r\n                                    Constructive trust is imposed by a court to prevent unjust enrichment or correct a wrongful act. It arises when someone holds property that they should not legally own, and the court imposes a trust to transfer the property to the rightful owner.\r\n                                </span>\r\n                            </div>\r\n                            \r\n                        </div>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                </div>\r\n'),
